com.googlecode.javastar

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.javastar.Node

  • public abstract class Node
extends Object
    Node classes should extend this abstract class. The reason this class exists is to enforce users to override the equals() and hashCode() methods because the algorithm heavily relies on them.
    Using good hashCode values means better performance of the algorithm.
    Author:
    Steven Roose
